---
title: Stir-fried Teriyaki Chicken Noodles with broccolini, bell pepper and paprika aioli
description: This tangy teriyaki stir-fry is a simple recipe the whole home is sure to love. Juicy bell peppers and tender broccolini add crunch and vibrancy to a colourful and filled-with-flavour dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R20_W47_IE_IEXFCLC0115-3_MAIN__14high-ee794d5f.jpg
